# Absolute path to the design-studio vault. Optional — if unset, the app reads
# ~/.design-studio-vault (the same pointer every design-studio skill uses).
# DESIGN_STUDIO_VAULT=/Users/you/hermes

# The command used to run a skill headlessly (Hybrid run). Optional.
# The active project slug and "/<skill-name>" are appended at runtime.
# CLAUDE_BIN=claude

# Opt-in: when set, creating a project from the dashboard "+" also fires
# design-studio-debrief round 1 as a headless background pass (drafts the
# restated problem, rubric, and clarification agenda). Off by default — it
# spawns a real Claude agent that writes the vault. Needs CLAUDE_BIN on PATH
# + authed and the design-studio skills installed.
# DESIGN_STUDIO_AUTORUN_DEBRIEF=1
